  "text": "On the other side, spliced XBP1 has been shown to upregulate various DNA damage response and repair genes suggesting that ER stress-and DNA repair mechanism might cooperate in genetically unstable cells to generate cancerous cells [CITATION_1] , by accumulating genetic defects through chromosomal rearrangements (causing loss-offunction of tumor suppressors or conferring additional proliferative advantages) that promote a state of increased aggressiveness [CITATION_2] .",
